snippet.title: Today's Takeaway
snippet.description:
Hi everyone,
Today’s Takeaway is a group of enthusiasts in science, nature, history, spirituality and so on.
We are interested in anything in this world that sounds hard to believe, and look to break down these myths into comprehensible explanations. 
But we tend not to keep it to ourselves, but spread the knowledge. This Youtube channel is part of that ambition. 
Subscribe us to see the most bizarre creatures in the wild, strangest events that happened among us, and most shocking historical facts that are not written in any ordinary textbooks. 
Like our videos if they help you somehow with your assignments or your own journey of discovery. 
❤️ Click here to SUBSCRIBE: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6dboYC0HgLSSPgRMJExfRA
And also, don’t hesitate to leave some comments letting us know if there are even more peculiar things people should know.
